QUOTE

1.How do I get a quote?

We can accept most of the 3D file formats like SolidWorks (.sldprt)/ ProE(.prt) / IGES(.igs) / STEP (.stp) / Parasolid (.x_t)/.stl. We can also use 2D drawing (.pdf) for quote against the parts with simple structure. All the other files formats are not listed above but can be read in SolidWorks/ProE/UG will be also fine.

2.What formats of the files can Premium Parts’ accept?

We can also use 2D drawing (.pdf) for quote against the parts with simple structure. All the other files formats are not listed above but can be read in SolidWorks/ProE/UG will be also fine.
